dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. North sheet includes inset of Leningrad. South sheet includes inset of "Baghdad to the Persian Gulf." Also shows railroads and steamship and ferry lines. Publisher's lists of maps, with prices, on inside of covers. Historic Maps copy imperfect: South sheet wanting.
